track_notes: Park at the Skoki Lodge parking lot and bike the first 3.9 kilometres along the gravel road to the Skoki Lodge trailhead (just above the Temple Lodge restaurant). Hike along the pleasant trail until you reach the fork towards the Hidden Lake campground. Hike along this trail past the tenting location to Hidden Lake. Scramble to just above the Richardon col and follow the ridge on scree to the summit. From Mount Richardson, hike down some scree blocks and snow to the Richardson-Pika col. Summiting Pika Peak is optional. From the col, follow a faint trail along the cliff band by the cliff. Before the second buttress, start heading upwards along slabby terrain with scree to the ridge of Ptarmigan Peak. For the descent, hike down to the left of the ascended ridge along scree to the alpine meadows below.
track_title: Mount Richardson, Pika Peak, Ptarmigan Peak Traverse
